snippet.title: Grand Theft Auto VI Trailer 2
snippet.description:
Vice City, USA.

Jason and Lucia have always known the deck is stacked against them. But when an easy score goes wrong, they find themselves on the darkest side of the sunniest place in America, in the middle of a criminal conspiracy stretching across the state of Leonida — forced to rely on each other more than ever if they want to make it out alive. 

Explore Vice City and beyond at https://www.rockstargames.com/VI

This trailer was captured entirely in-game from a PlayStation 5, comprised of equal parts gameplay and cutscenes.

Song: Hot Together
Artist: The Pointer Sisters
Written by Sharon Robinson

snippet.description: On a flight, a man didn’t want to sit next to a bigger guy, so he deliberately spilled his drink on the seat next to him. But when the larger man sat down, he didn’t even notice! The real shock came when the stewardess witnessed everything and moved the troublemaker to another seat. There, karma struck instantly, as a rowdy little boy kicked his seat non-stop! Watch this hilarious moment of instant karma unfold!

Σ’ αδιέξοδες βραδιές
Και με τέρμα γκάζι μπαίνω
Σ’ επικίνδυνες στροφές
Σε σκοινιά, λες, τεντωμένα
Συνεχώς ακροβατώ
Λες και τι δε λες για μένα
Μ’ άκου αυτό που θα σου πω
